### Admin stats
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Admin teachers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/teachers
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Admin students
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/students
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Create admin student WITHOUT group (groupPublicId optional)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/students
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin_student_no_group",
  "email": "admin.student.nogroup@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Create admin student WITH group
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/students
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin_student_with_group",
  "email": "admin.student.withgroup@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "groupPublicId": "{{group_public_id}}"
}

### Create admin student - validation fail (bad email)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/students
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "",
  "email": "invalid",
  "password": ""
}

### Update admin student assignment (with group)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/students/{{student_public_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin_student_updated",
  "email": "admin.student.updated@example.com",
  "groupPublicId": "{{group_public_id}}"
}

### Update admin student - unassign from group (null groupPublicId)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/students/{{student_public_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin_student_updated",
  "email": "admin.student.updated@example.com",
  "groupPublicId": null
}

### Update admin student - forbidden (TEACHER token)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/students/{{student_public_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{teacher_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "hacker_attempt",
  "email": "hacker@example.com"
}

### Admin achievements
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/achievements
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Admin achievement by code
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/achievements/FIRST_LESSON
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Create admin achievement
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/achievements
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "ADMIN_TEST_ACH_SAMPLE",
  "title": "Admin Test Achievement Sample",
  "description": "Created manually from .http",
  "icon": "icon",
  "color": "warning",
  "type": "LESSONS_COMPLETED",
  "threshold": 1,
  "active": true,
  "sortOrder": 999
}

### Update admin achievement
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/achievements/ADMIN_TEST_ACH_SAMPLE
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Admin Test Achievement Sample Updated",
  "description": "Updated manually from .http",
  "icon": "updated-icon",
  "color": "success",
  "threshold": 5,
  "active": true,
  "sortOrder": 1000
}

### Deactivate admin achievement
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/achievements/ADMIN_TEST_ACH_SAMPLE/active
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "active": false
}

### Admin achievement create - validation fail
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/achievements
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "bad-code",
  "title": "",
  "description": "Invalid payload",
  "icon": "icon",
  "color": "warning",
  "type": "AVATAR_CHANGED",
  "threshold": 1,
  "active": true,
  "sortOrder": -1
}
